      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 10:38:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普盟友班农因藐视国会入狱四个月后获释</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-29/trump-ally-steve-bannon-to-be-released-after-serving-4-months-in-prison-for-contempt-of-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约（美联社）——唐纳德·特朗普的长期盟友史蒂夫·班农于周二凌晨从联邦监狱获释，并立即恢复了对前总统的全力支持，敦促共和党人在下周大规模出现，击败民主党候选人副总统卡马拉·哈里斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-29/trump-ally-steve-bannon-to-be-released-after-serving-4-months-in-prison-for-contempt-of-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 04:08:27 GMT</pubDate>
